The paper deals with the management of hybrid memory systems, which is a topic related to computer architecture and operating systems. Therefore, cs.AR (Architecture), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.OS (Operating Systems) are likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses data placement and optimization, which is a topic related to databases, making cs.DB (Databases) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a mechanism to improve system performance, which is a topic related to systems and control, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible sub-category as well.
